description: {"blocks":[{"key":"dhla1","text":"Aim: the genotyping is used to identify if mice are heterozygote (hetero) or Wild-Type (WT), and the aim of the work is to validate the digestion method, and PCR program, the PCR primers, and the interpretation of the results.
